			<body><div id="53--magnanimity-baffled">

				<pb facs="/images/battle-pieces-v1/battle-pieces-i-0164.jpg"/>
				<head type="main">
				<hi rend="italic">Magnanimity Baffled.</hi>
				</head>
<lg>
<l>&quot;<hi rend="smallcaps">Sharp</hi> words we had before the fight;</l>
<l rend="4em">But—now the fight is done—</l>
<l>Look, here&apos;s my hand,&quot; said the Victor bold,</l>
<l rend="4em">&quot;Take it—an honest one!</l>
<l n="5">What, holding back? I mean you well;</l>
<l rend="2em">Though worsted, you strove stoutly, man;</l>
<l>The odds were great; I honor you;</l>
<l rend="6em">Man honors man.</l>
</lg>
<lg>
<l>&quot;Still silent, friend? can grudges be?</l>
<l n="10" rend="4em">Yet am I held a foe?—</l>
<l>Turned to the wall, on his cot he lies—</l>
<l rend="4em">Never I&apos;ll leave him so!</l>
<l>Brave one! I here implore your hand;</l>
<l rend="2em">Dumb still? all fellowship fled?</l>
<l n="15">Nay, then, I&apos;ll have this stubborn hand!&quot;</l>
<l rend="2em">He snatched it—it was dead.</l>
</lg>

</div></body>
